Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮 祈里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.62,0:02:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}新娘人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候没有察觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈瞳孔中那诡异的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给鲤鱼喂食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情交给下人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不干家务活也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免感冒你先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胖了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.10,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你胖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不允许胖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.00,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起风了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燥热夹杂着阴冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的夜里总有人哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 祈里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.40,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情平静了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.60,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈也不是恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她觉得氏家的新娘一定要漂亮地嫁进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且重要的展览会又在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑陋 那么丑陋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.40,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是日本引以为傲的优秀人偶制作师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也嫁到了不得了的人家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只要有幸雄在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天也要早起 休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可能是疲劳了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按摩的话你跟我说我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在镜月院学过 还算拿手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的事就忘记吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不必做那些事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是重要的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 让我做点什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我嫁过来就像是客人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天你来做早饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄 早饭做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈里 我应该说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不干家务活也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 祈里也趁热快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我给祈里准备了别的东西吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人稍微胖了一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说坐下你听不见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把背挺起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身边的事无论什么下人都会做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就安安静静地坐着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽 婀娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 祈里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄 救救我 请救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 祈里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人说让你清醒一下头脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除内心的杂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的杂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上衣服试试吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼神还没有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还不能称为死亡人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会与寿服相称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是充满了悲哀与绝望的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 果然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 你又
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 在哭的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约是高中生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像人偶一样美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.10,0:10:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮 祈里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安安静静地坐着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怕什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就一直被那个人注视着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候开始就一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了到我们家来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都为我高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.60,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个孤儿能嫁到那么好的人家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨的是那家的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女也一直这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要坚持吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想让别人不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是当事人的希望对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下指明方向才是大人的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是大人不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 我擅自出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你很想逃走才出来的 不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧 在这里不妙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 已经不哭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么你知道我在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是虽然不知道不过能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁和地狱少女联系上的话我就能感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无论如何都要送谁下地狱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过诅咒他人最终自己也要下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己下地狱无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不能让镜月院的各位流泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜月院就是这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在这里成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的时候曾想尽早看看外面的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却觉得这里好亲切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.30,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后支持着我们的家的是氏家镜月老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也祝福我嫁入她家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却在忍受着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不被允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让我像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.70,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不是你一个人解决的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你和这里的人好好谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说的话能体谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话我肯定会都说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么难过的事的话随时都可以回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里的人真的都很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很珍惜我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不忍的话这个家就没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你找了地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出口是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急的时候谁都可以用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说紧急出口就是地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有我们可以做到的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人帮你才跟我们来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不会解开绳子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她最看重这里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲自己 好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后她一定也会很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 祈里她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 今天可以退下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.20,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去散步了一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.70,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 因为你的腿很能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人偶不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双腿不能动就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人偶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我希望的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶不需要有心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双眼多么漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是死亡人偶的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了啊　女人好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在才明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请原谅我修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能祈祷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能忏悔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把人当人 而像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会痛 会愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能成为那个人的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.30,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈里 你在和谁说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和幸雄生活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也老了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.80,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是胜不了年纪的 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你羡慕人偶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远美丽不会变老的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你死的那么简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你痴迷人偶是无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人可不是人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人偶比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人简直就是既肤浅又丑陋的歪门邪道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶才是我的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 人偶的生死都由我掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该小姐上场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮 就像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想做一个 像你一样的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定和寿服很相配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你永远在那个世界里做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.60,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过模特只是你自己的死态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.90,0:22:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄 今后我会连妈妈的份一起好好待你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身与心都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.90,0:22:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一直看着我就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.60,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终还是个可悲的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人间地狱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.00,0:23:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
