Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.96,0:24:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本故事纯属虚构\N登场人物名 团体名等全部与现实无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.50,0:24:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.40,0:24:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路 多 隆菲尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.00,0:24:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从地狱回来的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.00,0:24:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.50,0:24:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.70,0:24:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不认为你比我有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.60,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也有事想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.90,0:24:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
